<div class="col-10 offset-1">
<div class="biography">
  <div class="text-center">
    <h1>- My biography -</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<br />
<br />

<div class="row">  
    <div class="col-sm-4">      
      <%= image_tag 'ivan.jpg', class: 'rounded-circle img-fluid' %>      
    </div>
 
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="me">      
        <p> My name is Ivan Bustos. I am from Monterrey, Mexico. Currently, I am working in the intelligence department at Orange investments. Basically, my job is to make research and come up with a hypothesis on what to do with a piece of land. Web development is one of my passions, that is why I joined to The Firehose Project. I have some ideas that want to turn them into projects.
        </p>
      </div>      
    </div> 
  </div>  
</div>

<br class="clear" />
<br />
<hr>
